version_description:
Fixed an issue affecting playback of downloaded content for some users.
If you experienced issues playing downloaded content, please launch the app while online at least once and try to play the contents.

Fixed an issue affecting playback of downloaded content for some users.
If you experienced issues playing downloaded content, please launch the app while online at least once and try to play the contents.

This release includes improvements on the details page and a new Ways to Watch section on how you can enjoy your favourite movies and TV series.
This release supports iOS 8 devices, however, future updates will require iOS 9 or latter. If you have an iOS 8 device, please update to the latest iOS release so you can continue to receive Sky Store updates.

- New autoplay feature for TV Boxsets - automatically plays the next episode after you finish viewing the current, perfect, for binge viewing your favourite TV series.
- Support for iOS 11.
- Bug fixes and performance improvements
